        <h2>What is this app about?</h2>
        <p>This is a simple Express app using EJS for templating. It demonstrates how to create, read, update, and delete data (CRUD operations) using form submissions and JavaScript. The app also lets you download an image, and includes some simple routing.</p>
        
        <h3>Features of this app:</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Create, read, update, and delete data</li>
            <li>Form handling with JavaScript</li>
            <li>Static file serving (CSS and images)</li>
            <li>File download functionality</li>
        </ul>
        
